|DATA EXPORTED FROM HORNRESP - RESONANCES NOT MASKED

|COMMENT: NEW RECORD - AIYIMA Cu  taped horn

|~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

|REQUIRED AKABAK SETTINGS:

|File > Preferences > Physical system constants:

|Sound velocity c = 344m/s
|Medium density rho = 1.205kg/m3

|Sum > Acoustic power:

|Frequency range = 10Hz to 20kHz
|Points = 533
|Input voltage = 2.86V rms
|Integration = 2Pi-sr
|Integration steps = 1 degree ... 1 degree
|Integration method = Cross

|~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Def_Const |Hornresp Input Parameter Values
{
|Length, area and volume values converted to metres, square metres and cubic metres:

S1  =    60.00e-4;  |Horn segment 1 throat area (sq m)
S2  =    81.34e-4;  |Horn segment 1 mouth area and horn segment 2 throat area (sq m)
S3  =   621.41e-4;  |Horn segment 2 mouth area and horn segment 3 throat area (sq m)
S4  =   686.49e-4;  |Horn segment 3 mouth area (sq m)

L12 =    20.00e-2;  |Horn segment 1 axial length (m)
L23 =   250.00e-2;  |Horn segment 2 axial length (m)
L34 =    20.00e-2;  |Horn segment 3 axial length (m)

Vrc =    20.00e-3;  |Rear chamber volume (cubic m)
Lrc =    20.00e-2;  |Rear chamber average length (m)

Ap  =    38.00e-4;  |Rear chamber port cross-sectional area (sq m)
Lpt =    10.00e-2;  |Rear chamber port tube length (m)

Vtc = 10000.00e-6;  |Throat chamber volume (cubic m)
Atc =   531.00e-4;  |Throat chamber cross-sectional area (sq m)

|Parameter Conversions:

Sd  = 531.00e-4;  |Diaphragm area (sq m)

Arc = Vrc / Lrc;

Ltc = Vtc / Atc;
}
|~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

|Network node numbers for this tapped horn system:

|               0-Voltage-1
|                         |
|           -Chamber-5-Driver-6-Chamber-7-Port-
|          |                                   |
|8-Segment-9-Segment---------------------------10-Segment-11-Radiator

|~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Def_Driver 'Driver'

  Sd=531.00cm2
  Bl=29.06Tm
  Cms=1.09E-04m/N
  Rms=9.66Ns/m
  fs=42.00Hz  |Mmd = 124.70g not recognised by AkAbak, fs calculated and used instead
  Le=1.40mH
  Re=5.10ohm
  ExpoLe=1

System 'System'

  Driver Def='Driver''Driver'
    Node=1=0=5=6

  Duct 'Throat chamber'
    Node=5=9
    SD={Atc}
    Len={Ltc}
    Visc=0

  Duct 'Rear chamber'
    Node=6=7
    SD={Arc}
    Len={Lrc}
    Visc=0

  Duct 'Rear chamber port'
    Node=7=10
    SD={Ap}
    Len={Lpt}
    Visc=0

  Waveguide 'Horn segment 1'
    Node=8=9
    STh={S1}
    SMo={S2}
    Len={L12}
    Conical

  Waveguide 'Horn segment 2'
    Node=9=10
    STh={S2}
    SMo={S3}
    Len={L23}
    Conical

  Waveguide 'Horn segment 3'
    Node=10=11
    STh={S3}
    SMo={S4}
    Len={L34}
    Conical

  Radiator 'Horn mouth'
    Node=11
    SD={S4}
